  <description type="morphology">Plants 1–15 cm. Leaf blades ob-lanceolate, margins entire or toothed, faces sericeous (silvery), sometimes sparsely stipitate-glandular as well. Ray florets 0. Disc florets 7–26; corollas yellow, 6–11 mm. 2n = 34, 36.</description>
